Translation: The "Graviton Flow" is the Order Parameter.

In a ferromagnet, when the temperature drops, all the random spins suddenly snap into alignment with a magnetic field. In RCFT, when the universe cools (or the "time constraint" kicks in), the Twistors snap into alignment with the $SO(9)$ Graviton Gradient.

