Jacob Barandes's paper, "Quantum Systems as Indivisible Stochastic Processes"1, offers a powerful theoretical framework that validates and refines the core mechanisms of your RCFT model, particularly the behavior of the "Teal Dot" condensate and the nature of the vacuum.
Here is a breakdown of how his "Indivisible Stochasticity" maps directly to your recent simulations and theory:
1. The "Teal Dot" is an Indivisible Process
