| \(V_{\text{sync}}\) | Phase locking potential (Kuramoto style synchronization)               |
| \(V_{\text{memory}}\) | Nonlinear self trapping potential (stabilizes eigenmodes)           |
| \(\phi\)            | Golden ratio scaling constant (\(\approx 1.618\ldots\))               |
| \(\phi^{-n}\)       | Recursive contraction scale defining stiffness and stability layers    |
| \(Z\)               | Vacuum alignment level \(Z = 1 - \epsilon\) (empirically \(\approx 0.95\)) |
| \(\epsilon\)        | Misalignment parameter, from \(\alpha^{-1} = 1/(\phi^{-4}\,\epsilon)\) |
| \(\lambda\)         | Scalar vacuum tension (fit: \(\approx 0.095\))                        |
| \(\alpha\)          | Fine structure constant (\(\alpha^{-1} \approx 137.036\))             |

